data.description: ** ROOF TO BE REPLACED PRIOR TO CLOSING ** Loads of natural light shine through the airy atmosphere of this home's open concept kitchen/living area, with its high ceilings and spacious design. This split plan is quiet and cozy, with plenty of room to entertain and to spread out even when gathering in the common areas, around which the rest of the home centers. The sellers have enjoyed the neighborhood and have found great tranquility here, and they are sure you will find this to be a great place to live. It's a perfect combination of privacy and close proximity to shopping, restaurants and services, with Bayside Lakes Blvd. a very short drive away. The kitchen boasts beautiful Viscount granite tops, white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, pantry, eat-in bar and an island, with plenty of cabinet space for your culinary wares. In the main living areas, you will find laminate flooring, with vinyl wood-look plank in the master bedroom. The master also has a roomy shower, soaking tub, and separate wc, along with a huge closet. Out back, you will love the screened porch and pavered patio with embedded lights and fire pit, a great place to spend the evenings with your favorite people. New AC in and out, new water softener. Hurry! This one is going to be popular! Schedule your exclusive viewing today!
